Package: changepointtool
Type: Package
Title: Fixed-Segment Change-Point Detection with Gurobi
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jiaqi", "Lei", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a mixed-integer optimization model for fixed-segment
    change-point detection based on segmented empirical cumulative distribution
    functions. The optimization model is solved with the Gurobi R interface.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports:
    Matrix,
    gurobi
SystemRequirements: Gurobi Optimizer and a valid Gurobi license
